## 7. 캐시 Key 전략 설계

| 캐시 이름 | Key 패턴 | 예시 |
|----------|---------|------|
| userProfile | `userProfile::userId:{userId}` | `userProfile::userId:abc-123` |
| userSettings | `userSettings::userId:{userId}` | `userSettings::userId:abc-123` |
| productList | `productList::active` | `productList::active` |
| followCount | `followCount::userId:{userId}` | `followCount::userId:abc-123` |
| feedList | `feedList::userId:{userId}::page:{page}` | `feedList::userId:abc-123::page:0` |
| notification | `notification::userId:{userId}` | `notification::userId:abc-123` |

