## 9. 캐시 모니터링 설정

```kotlin
// domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/config/CacheMetricsConfig.kt
@Configuration
class CacheMetricsConfig {

    /**
     * Spring Actuator + Micrometer로 캐시 히트율 모니터링
     * /actuator/caches 엔드포인트 활성화
     */
    @Bean
    fun cacheMetrics(
        cacheManager: CacheManager,
        meterRegistry: MeterRegistry,
    ): CacheMetricsRegistrar {
        return CacheMetricsRegistrar(meterRegistry, emptyList(), listOf(cacheManager))
    }
}
```

```yaml
# application.yml 추가
management:
  endpoints:
    web:
      exposure:
        include: health, info, caches, metrics
  metrics:
    cache:
      instrument:
        auto: true
```

